overview.en: Cred is a decentralized global lending platform that facilitates open access to credit anywhere and anytime，harness the power of blockchain to allow everyone to benefit from low-cost credit products.
overview.zh: Cred是一个基于区块链和加密数字货币的金融生态系统，帮助全球的加密数字货币用户，随时随地高效地享受各类金融服务，比如理财CredEarn和借贷CredBorrow。
